Shocking footage has emerged of a man stabbing a bouncer outside a Melbourne nightclub . 
  Police say the man had been ejected from the club late Thursday night when he soon returned and attacked the security guard from behind . 
  The 29-year-old bouncer was taken to hospital with non-life threatening injuries . 
  In a separate incident on Good Friday another security guard was stabbed in the leg . 
  Police have described the incident as 'disgusting'